P WITH бON THE INNER CIRCLE AND OBSERVE THE CODE THROUGH THROUGH THE WINDOW.  иN THECASE OF MULTIPLE WINDOWS, HE WOULD HAVE BEEN GIVEN а, б, AND ц, ROTATED ASBEFORE TO LINE UP а AND б AND LOOK THROUGH WINDOW ц FOR THE ANSWER.  сUCH ISTHE CASE WITH нEUROMANCER.         тHE CODE WHEEL IN нEUROMANCER IS USED TO OPERATE THE паь MACHINEFOUND AT VARIOUS LOCATIONS THROUGHOUT THE GAME.  ыOU WILL BE GIVEN THREEACCESS CODES AND ASKED FOR A VERIFICATION CODE.  тHERE ARE 16 POSSIBLE а'S,б'S AND ц'S.  тHE CODES ARE BROKEN DOWN INTO TWO TABLES.  тHE FIRST TABLESGIVES а (OUTER RING) AND б (INNER RING), TO BE CROSS REFERENCED TO EACH OTHERTO GET A POSITION NUMBER. тHIS POSITION NUMBER WILL BE CROSS REFERENCED WITH ц(WINDOWS) TO GIVE THE 3 TO 6 DIGIT VERIFICATION CODE.  тHE ACCESS CODES YOUWILL BE GIVEN ARE LISTED BELOW WITH тхрее леттерс ин уппер цасе (USUALLY THEFIRST THREE, BUT NOT ALWAYS, SO и HAVE TRIED TO DRAW YOUR ATTENTION TO THEONES THAT DO NOT HAVE THE FIRST THREE IN CAPS).  тHESE WILL CORRESPOND TO THEABBREVIATIONS IN THE TABLES.  гOOD LUCK!       а                        б                         ц---------------          ---------------           ---------------нигHT CITY NEWS          емпEROR NORTON            асаNO COMPUTINGцхаTSUBO                 цыбERJACK                 спаCEDOCKцыбERSPACE               ратZ                      спACE цOLONY <--гемEINSCHAFT             холOGRAFIX                флаTLINEцраZY EDO                ларRY MOE                 зиоN CLUSTERмицROSOFTS               паь                       марCUS GARVEYцхеAP HOTEL              скиLL CHIPS               црыPTOLOGYйулIUS DEANE             схиN'S PAWN               аи (ONLY TWO LETTERS)донUT WORLD              генTLEMAN LOSER           банK OF BERNEлавBOT                   мааS BIOLABS              баNK OF зURICH <--датABASE                 йусTICE BOOTH             цхиBA CITYсхиVA                    цыBERдECK <--             фуйI ELECTRICфреESIDE             